name: Travlogue.com
overview:
Travlogue is Indonesia social travel media for travelers to share travel experiences by posting stories and uploading photos or write travel reviews.

Travelers could ask questions and recommend travel advices about hotels, restaurants and best places to other travelers and help them to plan a trip.

Travelers can search and connect to others or friends nearby or even meet them in same location.

Travlogue is based on crowdsourcing content from its users, and will be the first social travel in Indonesia that allow travelers to connect each others by uploading photos and stories and let other users or friends to interact.

Travlogue can be very helpful for travelers who need advices and recommendation about destination places they wish to go, travelers also will be warned by others about scams/frauds that should be avoided.
